                                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                          "width": "fill_container",
                                          "content": "General podcast apps optimize playback controls and discovery, but the market lacks broad AI-transcription-driven semantic removal of ads, intros, and filler. This leaves a high-value niche for privacy-first, creator-aligned efficiency products.",
